t-ng-c932945091="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Analyzing content <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> I am now synthesizing the key information I've gathered from across your Workspace. My objective is to connect the dots between different sources, identify overarching themes, and build a foundational understanding that will inform the final research plan. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Generating research plan <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Now that I have a foundational understanding from the available information, I am constructing a tailored research plan. This strategy will guide my next steps, ensuring I investigate the most critical areas to fully address your request. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Here's my plan to tackle that topic. Let me know if you need to make changes. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Enhancing AI Coding Agent Independence <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Research Websites and Files <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (1) Research architectures for autonomous AI agents specifically designed for software engineering, focusing on concepts like 'Agentic Workflows' and 'loop-based' reasoning. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (2) Investigate methods to enhance the 'smartness' and reasoning capabilities of LLMs, such as: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (a) Chain-of-Thought (CoT) prompting <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (b) Tree of Thoughts <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (c) Reflexion and self-correction mechanisms <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (3) Explore technical implementations for giving AI agents 'independence' through Tool Use and Function Calling, specifically access to: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (a) Command-line interfaces (CLI) and terminals <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (b) File system reading and writing <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (c) Compilers and interpreters for code execution <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (d) Web search for real-time documentation <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (4) Find information on integrating Long-Term Memory and Context Management (e.g., Vector Databases, RAG) to allow the agent to retain knowledge of a codebase or project history without repetitive prompting. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (5) Research multi-agent frameworks (e.g., AutoGen, CrewAI, LangGraph) where different personas (e.g., Coder, Reviewer, Architect) collaborate to solve complex tasks autonomously. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (6) Analyze best practices for implementing 'Human-in-the-loop' safeguards while maximizing autonomous behavior for coding tasks. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> (7) Synthesize the findings to create a technical roadmap for upgrading the provided persona from a reactive text generator to a proactive, independent coding age sound interesting? <!----><!----><!----></p><!----></div><button _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" mat-icon-button="" aria-label="Expand" mattooltip="Expand text" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger expand-button mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="224552;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_0120b15e30532b4d&quot;,&quot;c_a093be25651b444b&quot;,null,null,null,null,null,null,1,null,null,null,1]];mutable:true" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-797" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c932945091="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-l google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></span><!----><!----></span><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!--